Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:09.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}成长过于迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}虽然明白他有非同一般的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}但仅凭这样不足以解释
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:28.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}原因果然是这个没有听说过的稀有技能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:32.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}憧憬一途 也就是对那个叫华伦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:35.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}技能的效果 早熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:37.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}只要坚持着信念 效果就会持续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}凭着信念的深度 效果就会强化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}算什么信念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔这个轻浮的家伙 超轻浮的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:45.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8\pos(640,53)}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:50.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}但能把真实的数值告诉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我想要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:01:00.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}技能还有别的神在盯着 不能告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔 今天能口头告诉你成长数值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:07.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:18.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我要帮助这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我的数值 升的那么快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:03:00.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}嗯 你现在正以惊人的速度成长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}换句话说 也就是成长期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:03.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}但这只不过是我的个人见解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我认为你有才能 你一定会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:15.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}而且你也试图要变得比现在更强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:16.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我会尊重你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}给你加油 给你帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}也会借你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}所以希望你和我约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不要再逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:33.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}拜托你 请不要留下我孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是 不会再乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}为了变强我会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}绝不会让神明大人变成孤独一人 让你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}听你这句话我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}于是 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}从今晚开始会有两三天不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:55.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}前几天没付账就擅自跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这是欠的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}特意跑来付钱 真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:20.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不过你要是不来 我就打算亲自去找你算账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}别再道歉了 贝尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我非常高兴看到您能再来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}今天也要去地下城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这个是便当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不 怎么好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}请收下 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不好意思 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好好感谢希儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}包括我在内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:55.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}多亏她帮你说好话 我们这些气血方刚的人才能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:02.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}小子 冒险者就是个只会装帅的没用职业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}最开始只要拼命活下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:10.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}境遇凄惨也好 被人嘲笑也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}活着回来的人就是人生赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我都说到这份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}千万别那么轻易倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}快 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}否则妨碍我做生意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是 我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:33.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}终于说我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}感谢诸位莅临聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我就是迦尼萨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:59.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这次的宴会也有这么多同伴出席 迦尼萨超感激
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8\pos(640,53)}哟 几百年不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8\pos(640,53)}嗯 四天不见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:04.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}在那里那个面相很差的人 是叫建御雷神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:08.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}赫尔墨斯也在啊 那家伙旅行完回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}喂 来了 美之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}真让人受不了 居然活在人间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}晚上好 赫斯缇雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}打扰到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我尤其不擅长和你打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我最喜欢你这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}其实你算还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}芙蕾雅 小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}咦 洛基来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么 没事我就不能来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:59.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不过正好 洛基 我有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}什么 小矮子有事问我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:10.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你眷族里的剑姬 叫华伦什么的有正在交往的人或伴侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}白痴 艾丝是我家的心头好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:17.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}敢惹她的麻烦就碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你们两个关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:28.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}对了 说的有点晚了 洛基今天的打扮很不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好久不见你穿礼服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:35.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}算是吧 因为事先知道某个小矮子会来参加宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:39.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}想来嘲笑一下连礼服都买不起的穷酸神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}哼 还真是滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}为了嘲笑我而来被嘲笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:52.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么回事 那个穷酸的胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}果然大家的装备都很上乘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}今年都迎来那个时节了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怪物祭吗 一年转眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}加油 继续干下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:31.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}萝莉巨乳对战洛基贫胸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我用一万巴利斯赌巨乳胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我用十个圣灵剂赌贫胸最后一不留神击败巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:44.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}被狠狠教训的洛基大人 我会好好安慰她的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}今天先暂时到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:52.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}看着你那贫胸 我根本就没把你放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}吵死了 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你俩又打架了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}赫菲斯托斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:02.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}幸好我来了 我正想见你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}想见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:08.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}事先声明 我一个巴利斯也不会借给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:13.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}没礼貌 我看上去像那种会贪图好友钱包的神明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:18.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}还好意思说 三番五次借宿在我眷族家中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:23.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}最后赶你走 某人却哭闹说自己没地方住 没钱没工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}会被想像成那样也是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}确实过去的我是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不过现在已经不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}因为我找到了自己的眷族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}原来如此 是叫贝尔的小子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那个白发红眼的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}有了自己的眷族后 也有不少神明改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:51.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}赫菲斯托斯 赫斯提亚 我也差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这么快？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:57.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}嗯 本来有件事想确认一下 但也确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}况且我对这里的男人们都腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那么 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:07.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}话说你找我有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}依据内容 我不否认会斩断我们近邻的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我当然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}为了贝尔 请你制造一把武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这不是贝尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:33.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}米尔哈大人抱歉 我根本没打算买
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:40.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}米尔哈大人没去参加神明大人的宴会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:44.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}嗯 我收到邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:48.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不过由于眷族弱小的关系 我忙于调配物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔 拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}万万不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么 身为好邻居奉承一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}今后也请多多关照我的眷族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你打算跪到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}别看我这样 其实还是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你跪在那里 害我无法集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:23.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:37.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}并非自夸 你知道我眷族制造的物品值多少钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我知道价格昂贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:43.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那么存够钱 再来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}必须是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}拜托你了 赫菲斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}话说你这身打扮 到底算怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我在下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:06.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}建御雷神教我的谢罪和求人方法的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那小子尽教些无谓的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}赫斯提亚 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}为什么要做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:15.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我想助贝尔一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那孩子正在试图改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}找到唯一奋斗的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}即便是道路崎岖 他也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}因为是一条危险之路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:31.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}所以我想帮他 给他一把能披荆斩棘的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}他总是在帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:39.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}他一个劲儿养活我 我明明是他的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}却没为他做过一件神明像样做过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我讨厌不能为他做点什么的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}正试图改变自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:59.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好吧 我会帮你那孩子做一把武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:03.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}谢谢你 赫菲斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}丑话说前头 这钱你还是要付的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}即便用几十年几百年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}嗯 知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你那孩子最擅长的武器是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是短刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}难道赫菲斯托斯由你亲自出马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:30.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那是当然 我和你的私人交情怎么能把眷族牵扯进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}厉害 你在天界也算是闻名的神匠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}没想到能由你亲自操刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:40.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你没忘记吧 这里不是天界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:44.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我们根本无法使用神力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:49.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我不管 能由你亲手锻造是我最高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你也过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}作为助手 给我好好干活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}嗯 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:08.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}成为冒险者仅半个月 为他锻造一把什么样的一级武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那么 我该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:16.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}说是要出门两三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人今天也不回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}等一下 白发少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:36.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}所以呢 我希望你把这个钱包交给丢三落四的希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:41.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}呃…抱歉 我听不懂你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}阿娘 你说的不够清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:46.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}克朗尼 大人也很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那么说明你是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:54.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}希望你把钱包送去给旷工去看怪物祭的希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}就算不一一说明 你也该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:58.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}当然希尔并非翘班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}有事先请假去看怪物祭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}眼下可能正为没带钱包而烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}拜托您了 克朗尼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}明白了 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:18.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}请问怪物祭是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:26.49,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}所谓怪物祭是每年一次由迦尼萨家族主办的超大型活动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:37.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}出场者一人独占竞技场 在观众面前驯服来自地下城的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:49.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}也就是说难度高和场面宏大的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这次你又暗地里谋划些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:16:00.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}还是看上哪个不起眼家族的小鬼想找他麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}真是的 总是喜欢到处埋下争端的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你这个痴汉女神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:19.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}太好啦 太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}谢谢你 赫菲斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我能现在就拿去给贝尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:36.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}无所谓 但别忘记还有债要还
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:37.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:44.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}说吧 这次你看上的小鬼是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:49.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}非常不靠谱 为一点小事就会哭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不过真的很漂亮 如此晶莹剔透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我从没见过的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:00.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}真的是很偶然找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}偶尔跑进我的视线而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不好意思 突然有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}什么 你怎么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8\pos(640,53)}下回再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}咦 帐也要我结啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么了 艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:25.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好厉害 和琉说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:35.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}要找希儿看来很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人 你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}可能是因为我想见你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是吗 我也很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:52.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}果然我们被非比寻常的羁绊联系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.33,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}那个…神明大人 到底去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我们约会吧 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}等一下 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}有人拜托我找人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是吗 那就一边约会一边找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:07.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}一箭双雕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}但也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}大叔 2个可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8\pos(640,53)}神 神明大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人 这不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:25.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么 你讨厌我吃过的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:29.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我怎么能吃神明大人那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.05,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}请吃我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你居然避开我 这次饶了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}帮我擦掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:43.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我看中你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:22.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不行 还想暂时守护那孩子的成长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:32.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你正在找一个女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔想的真周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:38.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}去追那个小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:51.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔 那家伙好像在看我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人 为什么那怪物会盯上你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}第一次见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}这里是戴纳街
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}只能进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:26.83,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.35,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:38.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:44.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我是男孩子吧 上吧 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:49.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么能不顾女孩 自己逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}仅凭我一人之力 无法保护神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}再这样下去会被追上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}怎么办才好 怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}对不起 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:42.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}我会争取时间 神明大人请快逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}你在说什么 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}立刻把这里打开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:54.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}神明大人 我已经不想再失去家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:00.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur8}贝尔！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
